_aLatestUpdates._sText:
-Added new CT spawn, giving players a new floor to explore

-Added more details around the map

-Changed some props position like the tank in CT spawn

-Fixed the lamp bug where it just flickered over and over again at light speed

-Added new hallway in the main floor, it connects the red hallway to the blue hallway where the stairs lead

I've decided to learn some new things with the source engine, I now know how to do arches and skyboxes, which I've added in my new counter strike source map :)

-Added Skybox

-Added Arch underneath toggle-able lamp hallway

-Changed a few textures around

-Added More Fog and Props

-Added More cover in the main hallway

-Added a balcony in the chandelier room

-Added Breakable Wood in the hostage area

-Removed 2 hostages and replaced it with 1 hostage at T spawn

-Added Door to T spawn

-Added Breakable Platform to stairs near T spawn

-Added 1 more lightswitch :)

-Made the stairway wider

-Made stairway door spawn open (because bots are stupid)

-Added a caged off stairway near CT spawn, next to purple light

-Added more lore to lights (some still light up for no reason, ill fix that later maybe)

_sText: STORY: Choppers have arrived and there right on top of us... guess they already found us. Alright men of arms, grab your weapons and defend the apartment! Leave 2 of them near the vending machines, and the other 2 in the basement. Remember, we can turn some lights off if we have to.
